# ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.medium

**Case**

Geo-tracking accuracy is average.

## Declaration

```swift
case medium
```

## Discussion

This value indicates that visual localization is complete and geo-tracking accuracy is average.

## Accuracies

- **ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.high**: Geo-tracking accuracy is high.
- **ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.undetermined**: Geo-tracking accuracy is undetermined.
- **ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.low**: Geo-tracking accuracy is low.
